Here's what I'll be looking for as the Senate considers filling the upcoming SCOTUS vacancy: I want someone who will apply the law impartially, not make the law;
Call balls &amp; strikes, not rewrite the rules of the game.
There's no room for judicial activism on the Supreme Court.

And I’ve never seen one of your bobcats outrun Isaiah Davis …
It’ll be a great game, that’s for sure.
@GoJacksFB!
